The mixed exercises provide comprehensive practice across all proportion skills covered in the lesson. Problems range from straightforward numerical proportions to proportions with variables on one or both sides, multi-step word problems, percent applications, map-scale questions, estimation tasks, and writing prompts that ask students to compare ratios and rates or create their own examples.

